           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mbckgr"
                                         using b                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se errore : uscita                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
            if       b-rsc                not  = spaces
                     go to exe-pgm-bkg-900.
